</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>
<num value="47">庚戌</num>
<pc>，</pc>吳以鎮海<term>節度使</term>徐溫為管內水陸馬步諸軍<term>都指揮使</term>
<pc>、</pc>兩浙都招討使<pc>、</pc>守侍中<pc>、</pc>齊國公<pc>，</pc>鎮<placeName>潤州</placeName>
<pc>，</pc>以<placeName>升</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>潤</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>常</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>宣</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>歙</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>池</placeName>
<measure quantity="6" unit="prefectures">
